{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"156e8eb4-3956-4499-b54d-19006b87fb8b","content":"Good news — in .NET 10, `dotnet test` uses Microsoft Testing Platform **by default**. The `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` property was the .NET 9 opt-in flag and is now redundant. You can safely remove it.\n\nYou **do** still need `EnableMSTestRunner` — that tells MSTest to build your test project as an MTP executable.","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01SbwfKtYEAV7EnP4Gfp5AKh","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Removing redundant property"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_016m7TAfcAtznF73LnGaS5Fq","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-be0e96294c474597bd7353d9fde9c047/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n    <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>","new_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-be0e96294c474597bd7353d9fde9c047/TestProject.csproj."}],"interactionId":"5fdcf75b-fe7d-480f-8884-594e01a1b888","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is on .NET 10 SDK (10.0.100) and wants to know about Microsoft Testing Platform (MTP) support. Let me provide accurate information.\n\nIn .NET 10, `dotnet test` uses Microsoft.Testing.Platform (MTP) by default — it's the new default test runner. The `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` property was needed in .NET 9 to opt in to the MTP-based `dotnet test` experience, but in .NET 10 it's no longer necessary because MTP is the default.\n\nSo the user can remove the `<TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>` line since it's redundant on .NET 10.\n\n\nHowever, they'll still need `<EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>` to use the MSTest runner, which compiles the test project as an executable that leverages MTP. Let me update the project file accordingly.","outputTokens":547,"requestId":"5C2C:196AFA:C10E5:F3099:69F54BEB"},"id":"a8f4ff1e-8b74-4791-a404-0953955c2419","timestamp":"2026-05-02T00:57:24.570Z","parentId":"6ff0f5a2-a0ad-49d6-8ddb-c5bf7d3c9f91"}
